{"title":"街上的树","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["贪心"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/475#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=475","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/475/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/475/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/475"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"某条街被划为 $n$ 条路段，这 $n$ 条路段依次编号为 $1\\dots n$。每个路段最多可以种一棵树。现在居民们给出了 $h$ 组建议，每组建议包含三个整数 $b,e,t$，表示居民希望在路段 $b$ 到 $e$ 之间至少要种 $t$ 棵树。这些建议所给路段的区间可以交叉。请问：如果要满足所有居民的建议，至少要种多少棵树。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"第一行为 $n$，表示路段数。\r\n\r\n第二行为 $h$，表示建议数。\r\n\r\n下面 $h$ 行描述一条建议：$b, e, t$，用一个空格分隔。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出只有一个数，为满足所有居民的建议，所需要种树的最少数量。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n9\r\n4\r\n1 4 2\r\n4 6 2\r\n8 9 2\r\n3 5 2\r\n```\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n5\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"$30\\%$ 的数据满足 $0<n\\le 1000$，$0<h\\le 500$；\r\n\r\n$100\\%$ 的数据满足 $0<n\\le 3\\times 10^4$，$h\\le 5000$，$0<b\\le e\\le 3\\times 10^4$，$t\\le e-b+1$。"}]}